description: Flowy and comfortable maxi dress with a vibrant floral print, perfect for summer days or beach outings. Features adjustable spaghetti straps and a relaxed fit. Made from breathable rayon fabric.
Handcrafted sterling silver necklace featuring a unique, intricately designed pendant with a hammered finish. Comes with an 18-inch delicate chain. A timeless piece for any occasion.
A versatile, essential denim jacket with a comfortable, slightly oversized fit. Made from premium, durable cotton denim. Perfect for layering over dresses or t-shirts all year round.
A beautiful set of three minimalist gold-plated rings designed for stacking or wearing individually. Adds a subtle touch of elegance. Available in sizes 6, 7, 8.
Lightweight and breathable linen blend trousers with a stylish wide-leg cut and an elastic waistband for ultimate comfort. Ideal for warm weather and relaxed elegance.
Unique stud earrings featuring natural, unpolished amethyst crystals. Each pair is one-of-a-kind. Set in hypoallergenic sterling silver posts. Perfect for adding a touch of natural beauty.
Cozy and soft knit cardigan with an open front design. Perfect for layering over blouses or t-shirts during cooler evenings. Made from a comfortable acrylic-wool blend.
An elegant bracelet featuring small, lustrous freshwater pearls strung on a delicate silver chain. Finished with a secure clasp. Perfect for everyday wear or special events.
